name: Birthday Cupcakes
description:
Annie’s Little Cupcakes are available in a selection of sponges - vanilla, lemon, chocolate and almond with a choice of vanilla, chocolate or lemon buttercream. Other flavours are available upon request.

Prices start at $3.00 each (minimum order of 6)

Great for birthday celebrations!

Mini cupcakes are also available, minimum order of 24 for $35
